Summary: One fluttering pulsing bluish light changing in intensity become 2-3, then back to 1
divs: sighting detailson way to store, saw light on a clear sky just before dawn, light did not look like a star. i stopped in road for a few minutes, observed what appeared to be 1 light turning into two lights, to 3 lights, all closely compacted together, back to 1 light, and repeating cycle.. clouds began to form around object though no other clouds in sky at the moment. clouds around object appeared displaced\fuzzy, but light shined through brightly. before clouds appeared (dura ration of cloud appearance was less than 3 minutes) object appeared to have jellyfish shape where smaller lights were where tentacles would be (if it actually were a jellyfish i'm the sky).
